       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. LEDGER.
       AUTHOR. PTA-11 LOG ENGINE.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT SCORE-FILE ASSIGN TO "scores.txt"
           ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  SCORE-FILE.
       01  SCORE-RECORD        PIC X(20).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DISPLAY-SCORE    PIC ZZZ9.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01  PASSED-SCORE        PIC S9(9) COMP-5.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PASSED-SCORE.
       000-MAIN.
           OPEN EXTEND SCORE-FILE
           MOVE PASSED-SCORE TO WS-DISPLAY-SCORE
           MOVE FUNCTION TRIM(WS-DISPLAY-SCORE) TO SCORE-RECORD
           WRITE SCORE-RECORD
           CLOSE SCORE-FILE
           GOBACK.
